### Create product
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/products
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Gold Necklace",
  "sku": "NK001",
  "vendorId": 1,
  "categoryId": 3,
  "basePrice": 1500.00,
  "sellingPrice": 1299.00,
  "metalType": "GOLD_PLATED",
  "occasion": "WEDDING",
  "gender": "WOMEN"
}

### Search by name
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/products/search?name=gold

### Featured products
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/products/featured

### Filter by metal and price
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/products/filter?metalType=GOLD_PLATED&minPrice=1000&maxPrice=5000
